column5: I have taken over the past two weeks at a lake i have been fishing right across the street from me. As a few of you know i love to take photo's and sunsets as you can see are my favorite.              This one is of the beach here in dover taken a little over a week ago.
Nice pics Nauti. You have a good eye. The reflection on pic #4 is very nice.  Hookset.
WOW, gorgeous pictures!! Nothing more beautiful than nature!
Nice pics, you have a good eye for framing pics. You should try to sell a couple to a post card company, you might actually get paid a few bucks for doing something you love to do.
Thanx alot guy's & yes stoty could not agree more.  Uncle buck never thought about that actually and would not even know where to start!  Here are a couple more i have done.
Very nice shots you have talent,the only thing missing are the bikini clad perch fisherwomen.LOL
Love the pics Tracy.  I love sunsets and sunrises also.  I've got so many on my computer (mostly sunsets   ) its not even funny.  Joey
They ARE beautiful pictures....  Thanks for sharing...
beautiful nothing more to say about it
